name: NUTANHAT DEVELOPMENT SOCIETY
briefDescription: NUTANHAT DEVELOPMENT SOCIETY is situated in West Bengal, India and is in service for the development of the unpriviledged groups including  children and women from 1992. Present working area in Purulia district of West bengal and Sagar island of south 24 parganas. Has FCR since 1996 and is supported by foreign and Govt. organisations.
